{"id":248143,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2012/08/global-voices-伊朗、以色列两国公民同声：不想为你们的/","date":"2012-08-21T10:00:09Z","modified":"2012-08-21T10:00:09Z","title":"Global Voices | 伊朗、以色列两国公民同声：“不想为你们的战争而死”","content":"<p><p>从主流媒体的新闻标题看起来，伊朗和以色列就快爆发战争了。以色列政治人物持续<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-14/israel-plans-for-iran-strike-as-citizens-say-government-serious.html\" href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-14/israel-plans-for-iran-strike-as-citizens-say-government-serious.html\">威胁</a>要攻击伊朗的核子设施，而伊朗当局<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.jpost.com/IranianThreat/News/Article.aspx?id=281366\" href=\"http://www.jpost.com/IranianThreat/News/Article.aspx?id=281366\">重申</a>他们的旧日口号：以色列会“从地图上消失”。</p>\n<p>虽然双方都发出了战争的杂音，和平运动也没有缺席。</p>\n<p>最近以色列人在首都特拉维夫举行和平反战<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-14/israel-plans-for-iran-strike-as-citizens-say-government-serious.html\" href=\"http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-14/israel-plans-for-iran-strike-as-citizens-say-government-serious.html\">示威</a>，并利用網絡散发“对战争说不”的讯息。</p>\n<p> </p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=496546783706385&#038;set=a.401026863258378.107525.400704776623920&#038;type=3&#038;theater\"><img title=\"\"So once again, load and clear, we are saying NO to this war.\" From the Israeli-Loves-Iran Facebook campaign. \" src=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/08/israeliran1.jpg\" alt=\"\"So once again, load and clear, we are saying NO to this war.\" From the Israeli-Loves-Iran Facebook campaign. \" width=\"366\" height=\"416\" /></a></p>\n<p>“大声清楚的再说一遍，我们拒绝战争。”来自以色列人爱伊朗脸书活动。</p>\n</div>\n<p>爱好和平人士持续加入 2012 年三月十九日由以色列人 Pushpin Mehina（又名 Ronny）成立的<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.facebook.com/israellovesiran\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/israellovesiran\">脸书页面</a>，告诉伊朗人“<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2012/03/18/a-love-letter-from-israel-to-iran/\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2012/03/18/a-love-letter-from-israel-to-iran/\">以色列人爱你们，不会轰炸你们的国家</a>”。页面目前有超过七万人按“赞”。同一天伊朗人也成立了“<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.facebook.com/FromIranForPeaceAndDemocracy\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/FromIranForPeaceAndDemocracy\">来自伊朗，为了和平与民主</a>”，并很快发起了告诉以色列人“<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2012/03/21/iranians-to-israelis-we-are-your-friends/\" href=\"http://globalvoicesonline.org/2012/03/21/iranians-to-israelis-we-are-your-friends/\">我们是朋友</a>”的活动。</p>\n<p>当<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=496877740339956&#038;set=a.401026863258378.107525.400704776623920&#038;type=1&#038;theater\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=496877740339956&#038;set=a.401026863258378.107525.400704776623920&#038;type=1&#038;theater\">伊朗页面</a>转贴<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=496545977039799&#038;set=a.401026863258378.107525.400704776623920&#038;type=1&#038;theater\" href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=496545977039799&#038;set=a.401026863258378.107525.400704776623920&#038;type=1&#038;theater\">以色列页面</a>的以下留言，两个活动合流了：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>我们数百万人将受到伤害。会被征召入伍、被迫战斗、失去生命和亲人。我们这些来自特拉维夫和德黑兰的父母必须带着孩子避难，祈祷 飞弹不会打中我们。但是飞弹总会落下，落在某个人头上。这几天战争的声音更响了。所以在此大声清楚的再说一遍，我们拒绝战争。我们对伊朗人民说：我爱你 们。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>八月十六日星期三超过四百人签署一份網絡请愿书<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.haaretz.com/news/diplomacy-defense/hundreds-of-israelis-petition-idf-pilots-refuse-orders-to-bomb-iran.premium-1.458517\" href=\"http://www.haaretz.com/news/diplomacy-defense/hundreds-of-israelis-petition-idf-pilots-refuse-orders-to-bomb-iran.premium-1.458517\">请求</a>以色列战斗机驾驶当接到命令轰炸伊朗时予以拒绝。签署人中包括大学教授和人权捍卫者。</p>\n<p>網絡请愿书的<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"http://www.atzuma.co.il/tayasim\" href=\"http://www.atzuma.co.il/tayasim\">内容如下</a>：</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>各位空军驾驶员，我们认为攻击伊朗是极度错误的赌博，将给以色列带来极大的风险而且无法根本解决问题。就像之前说过的，就算攻击 行动再成功也无法阻止伊朗的核子计划，只能稍微拖延 —— 为了拖延这一点时间我们每个人都要付出高昂甚至惨痛的代价。各位空军驾驶员拥有比任何人更实际的力量来避免这场灾祸。</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div>校对：<a rel=\"nofollow\" title=\"使用者:Portnoy\" href=\"http://proj.daodin.net/mediawiki/index.php/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E8%80E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E3%80%81%E4%BB%A5%E8%89%B2%E5%88%97%E4%B8%A4%E5%9B%BD%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E5%90%8C%E5%A3%B0%EF%BC%9A%E2%80%9C%E4%B8%8D%E6%83%B3%E4%B8%BA%E4%BD%A0%E4%BB%AC%E7%9A%84%E6%88%98%E4%BA%89%E8%80%8C%E6%AD%BB%E2%80%9D&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F08%2F21%2F11373%2F&#038;description=&#038;via=sticker\" title=\"HEMiDEMi\"><span>HEMiDEMi</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://myshare.url.com.tw/index.php?func=newurl&#038;url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F08%2F21%2F11373%2F&#038;desc=%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E3%80%81%E4%BB%A5%E8%89%B2%E5%88%97%E4%B8%A4%E5%9B%BD%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E5%90%8C%E5%A3%B0%EF%BC%9A%E2%80%9C%E4%B8%8D%E6%83%B3%E4%B8%BA%E4%BD%A0%E4%BB%AC%E7%9A%84%E6%88%98%E4%BA%89%E8%80%8C%E6%AD%BB%E2%80%9D\" title=\"MyShare\"><span>MyShare</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.shouker.com/%22%20onclick=20js=document.createElement%20(\" title=\"Shouker\"><span>Shouker</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F08%2F21%2F11373%2F\" title=\"facebook\"><span>facebook</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://twitter.com/share?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F08%2F21%2F11373%2F&#038;text=%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E3%80%81%E4%BB%A5%E8%89%B2%E5%88%97%E4%B8%A4%E5%9B%BD%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E5%90%8C%E5%A3%B0%EF%BC%9A%E2%80%9C%E4%B8%8D%E6%83%B3%E4%B8%BA%E4%BD%A0%E4%BB%AC%E7%9A%84%E6%88%98%E4%BA%89%E8%80%8C%E6%AD%BB%E2%80%9D&#038;via=globalvoiceszh\" title=\"twitter\"><span>twitter</span></a> · <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://reddit.com/submit?url=http%3A%2F%2Fzh.globalvoicesonline.org%2Fhans%2F2012%2F08%2F21%2F11373%2F&#038;title=%E4%BC%8A%E6%9C%97%E3%80%81%E4%BB%A5%E8%89%B2%E5%88%97%E4%B8%A4%E5%9B%BD%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E5%90%8C%E